patthana11.15:1.1_0: Nasavitakkasavicāraṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naavitakkavicāramattaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naavitakkaavicāraṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:2.1_1: ārammaṇe sattacattālīsa …pe… purejāte āsevane chacattālīsa …pe… avigate aṭṭhacattālīsa.
patthana11.15:3.1_0: Napītisahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nasukhasahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naupekkhāsahagataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:4.1_0: Hetuyā ekūnapaññāsa …pe… purejāte āsevane aṭṭhacattālīsa …pe… avigate ekūnapaññāsa.
patthana11.15:5.1_0: Nadassanena pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabhāvanāya pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevadassanena nabhāvanāya pahātabbaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:6.1_1: ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:7.1_0: Nadassanena pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevadassanena nabhāvanāya pahātabbahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:8.1_1: ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:9.1_0: Naācayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naapacayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevācayagāmināpacayagāmiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:10.1_1: ārammaṇe sattarasa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekavīsa.
patthana11.15:11.1_0: Nasekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naasekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nanevāsekkhanāsekkhaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:12.1_1: ārammaṇe catuvīsa …pe… āsevane nava …pe… avigate ekūnatiṁsa.
patthana11.15:13.1_0: Naparittaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namahaggataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naappamāṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:14.1_1: ārammaṇe sattavīsa …pe… aññamaññe tiṁsa …pe… avigate bāttiṁsa.
patthana11.15:15.1_0: Naparittārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namahaggatārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naappamāṇārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)
patthana11.15:16.1_0: Nahīnaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namajjhimaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… napaṇītaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:18.1_0: Namicchattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nasammattaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naaniyataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ.)
patthana11.15:19.1_1: ārammaṇe sattarasa …pe… vipāke nava …pe… avigate ekavīsa.
patthana11.15:20.1_0: Namaggārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namaggahetukaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… namaggādhipatiṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)

patthana11.15:22.1_0: Naatītaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naanāgataṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
patthana11.15:23.1_0: Naatītārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… naanāgatārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… napaccuppannārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha ekūnapaññāsa.)
patthana11.15:24.1_0: Naajjhattaṁ naakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabahiddhā nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha dve.)
patthana11.15:25.1_0: Naajjhattārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …pe… nabahiddhārammaṇaṁ nakusalaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca …. (Saṅkhittaṁ. Sabbattha nava.)
